Did you know that by week 18 of pregnancy, a baby in the womb can hear sounds from the world around them? And by week 25 of pregnancy, babies can respond to the sound of someone’s voice with movement!

This is ANYTHING but a “clump of cells” – Join @TheIsabelBrown today as she explains how the 2nd trimester is FULL of life!

Tune into Freedom Seeds and get your ammo to win America’s culture war every day at 10 AM Pacific, 1 PM Eastern on IGTV, Facebook, Twitter and YouTube! 🇺🇸 #2ndTrimester #Abortion

node.title: The 2nd Trimester is Full of Life!
